corritors she answered Epyon's questions "Well sir, I..." said 
Starice "I don't sure if the baby is Alien or tf... you see, her body 
is too small, her beast mode is a fox but she isn't a biological 
fox... She (Describing the baby)... I guess that is other kind of 
Transformers... and I think that she's hungry... I found her around 
CF... Cordinates 2-6-5... "

"She behaves like a little tiny fox pup" added Starice "I don't know 
what to do..."

"I wonder if will be good idea give her biological food" Starice 
doubted a second "Sir... I know how deal with predacons, with 
decepticons... but anything preprared me to deal something like 
this..."
